"linenumber\">3</span>AMICO·OPTIMO<br id=\"al4-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">4</span>L·D·D·D</span></div><p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div></div>  <div id=\"facsimile-images\"><h2>Facsimile Images</h2></div>  <div id=\"apparatus\"><h4>Apparatus criticus</h4><ul><li><span><span>Text of CIL after Gualtherus</span></span></li></ul></div>  <div id=\"translation\"><h2>English translation</h2><p class=\"translation-author\"><a href=\"https://orcid.org/0000-0003-1030-5679\">Giorgia Capra</a></p>  <p>[...]ris Vitalis. Appius and Nicolaus (made this) for their excellent friend. Site granted by decree of the decurions.</p>  </div>  <div id=\"translation\"><h2>Italian translation</h2><p class=\"translation-author\"><a href=\"https://orcid.org/0000-0003-1030-5679\">Giorgia Capra</a></p>  <p>[...]ris Vitalis. Appius e Nicolaus (posero questo) per l'ottimo amico. Luogo concesso da un decreto dei decurioni.</p>  </div>  <div id=\"commentary\"><h2>commentary</h2>  <p>  </p></div>  <div id=\"bibliography\"><h2>bibliography</h2>  <ul><li></li><li> Gualtherus 1624 no. 233 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002388\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002388</a>  </li><li> Gualtherus 1624 [1625] no. 126 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001931\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001931</a>  </li><li> Castelli 1769 cl.14, no.9 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002084\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002084</a>  </li><li> Castelli 1784 cl.14, no.10 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002083\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002083</a>  </li><li> Mommsen 1883 <a href=\"http://arachne.uni-koeln.de/books/CILv10pII1883\" target=\"_blank\">7213</a>  <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000589\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000589</a></li></ul>  <ul><li></li></ul>  </div>  <div id=\"handnote\"> Line 1    Interlineation line 1 to 2    </div><div id=\"license\"> Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence. </div>",
